         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>b. l. 4, <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΣΤΡΗΦΟΣ</foreign>, <term xml:lang="la">lapis</term>; clearly a slip.</p>
            <p>b. l. 12, <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΕΤΥΜΟΣ</foreign> is presumably for <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἑτοῖμος</foreign>.</p>
